  "scenario": {
    "name": "Call Quality Degradation",
    "description": "Inject 30% packet loss on RTPEngine \u2014 the media relay for VoNR voice calls. RTP packets are dropped after RTPEngine receives them, degrading voice quality (MOS drop, jitter increase, audible artifacts). SIP signaling and 5G core are completely unaffected because they don't traverse RTPEngine. Tests whether the agent can diagnose a pure media-path fault without IMS signaling noise.",
